{"tid":1617885,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"共和黨參議員史葛收林鄭來函　斥只是空話不重視人權","createTime":"2019-10-04T02:34:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-05T03:22:30.000Z","uid":3204,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"9a67b0c75b4f6ef717f68aac8b92cdce62198df5","tid":1617885,"uid":3204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T02:34:57.000Z","msg":"【共和黨參議員史葛收林鄭來函 斥只是空話不重視人權】<br />\n<br />\n早前到香港觀察示威情況的美國共和黨參議員斯科特表示，收到行政長官林鄭月娥來函，批評內容空泛，只是更多的空話，不重視人權，更表明美國將致力協助港人抗爭，不會退縮。<br />\n<br />\n斯科特透露，曾經與林鄭月娥、商界領袖、泛民主派人士會面，形容林鄭月娥當時無法回答對於港人基本人權的疑問。到當地周四（10月3日）他再收到林鄭月娥的信件，林鄭月娥說珍惜自由民主及香港與美國的夥伴關係，又擔心美國國會推動《香港人權與民主法案》的不利影響。<br />\n<br />\n斯科特批評，信件內容只是更多的空話，顯示林鄭月娥不重視人權，包括拒絕市民和平集會的權利，又指當林鄭撰寫信件之時，正是香港青年為自由抗爭而胸膛中槍之日。<br />\n<br />\n全文︰<a href=\"http://www.passiontimes.hk/article/10-04-2019/56436\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.passiontimes.hk%2Farticle%2F10-04-2019%2F56436&d=beIwg85N8Ddzcl6rIyS0GbPkHgDHOcRHwLuXI7BMvHI%3D&h=cf0044d3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.passiontimes.hk/article/10-04-2019/56436</a><br />\n#共和黨 #參議員 #史葛 #林鄭月娥 #人權"},{"pid":"88098c7907ec6c9596987d9e50e2dd5f0f03c3ff","tid":1617885,"uid":163238,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T02:37:30.000Z","msg":"連美國議員都知條八婆淨係識講廢話<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7b0eed67398cbf20f1ba3263cfed131e3e310da","tid":1617885,"uid":3204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T02:48:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5e793df28aa6d46e702c647c1f41aa6920a9e4e","tid":1617885,"uid":193215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T07:21:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img sr